  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "HK XM8 5.56x45毫米突击步枪（FDE）",
      "en": "HK XM8 5.56x45 assault rifle (FDE)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "XM8",
      "en": "XM8"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "XM8是一款由H&K 于20世纪90年代研发的轻量化突击步枪系统，旨在替代M4步枪。尽管最终未被军方采用，但XM8仍不失为一把可靠、轻便且模块化的武器。它如何流入塔科夫市已无从考证，但这无疑是个令人欣喜的补充。沙色版本。",
      "en": "The XM8 is a lightweight assault rifle system developed in the 1990's by Heckler & Koch as a replacement for the M4. While it would ultimately not be accepted, the XM8 is a reliable, light, and modular weapon. How it came to Tarkov is unknown, but it is a welcome addition."
    },
    "weight": 2.275,
